    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface IChatMessage
extends IMessage
    A message only sent inside chatroom. Well-known chat messages are: TextMessage, AddMe, RemoveMe, CommandRequest, CommandResponse, InitUserRequest, InitUserResponse, ChatUserInfoRequest, ChatUserInfoResponse.
